==English==


===Etymology===
From Malay [[kĕris]]. Recognized as part of English ca. 1580.

===Noun===
'''kris'''
# An [[Indonesian]] or [[Malay]] [[dagger]] with a wavy, or ridgid serpentine blade.
# A [[Moro]] [[sword]] with an assymetrical blade.

